<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.7.8">
<l>nampaṉai ñālam paṭaittava ṉaittiru mārpaṉai</l>
<l>yumpa rulakiṉil yārkku muṇarvari yāṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>kumpi narakarka ḷēttuva rēlu mavarkaṇṭī</l>
<l>rempal piṟappiṭai tōṟen toḻukulan tāṅkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Supreme one, the creator of the world, the one with Śrī on [his] chest,</l>
<l>the one difficult to perceive for anyone in the world beyond,</l>
<l>those, see, who praise him, even if  they are from a hell of hot ashes,</l>
<l>are the clan we worship in each of our many births.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
